00:52:32.733 --> 00:52:33.860
Huwag kang mag-alala.

00:52:35.069 --> 00:52:38.531
Kung gagawin natin itong big deal,
mapapahiya lang ang pamilya natin.

00:52:39.490 --> 00:52:41.617
May sinabi
